title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 15 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 15 2021
description:
Where is Secretary of Transportation Pete Buttigieg... the world wonders. Psaki defends Biden WH Chief Klain's retweeting a post calling inflation a 'high-class problem.' Mom's call in on paternity leave. The seat fillers on The View try to impugn Joe Rogan. Chicago police union president tells officers to resist city vaccine mandate requirements: 'Hold The Line.' How much paternity leave is too much?
